g-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BA%A7n/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-h%E1%BB%99c-ch%C3%A2u/poem-sKlC0Bv2i3Le94tbeLVRBg">Nhất hộc châu - 一斛珠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BA%A7n/author-DkvIXCXm0ZOn-455t5I8ew">Giang Thái Tần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Qu%C3%A1-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C3%82m/poem-Bn6QZr-YLsw0EXi-VyEx-g">Quá Tương Âm - 過湘陰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-04/poem-0mGwjxx7W1KZvH2Ig15dKQ">Thủ 04 - 首０４</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-L%E1%BB%87nh-N%C4%83ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%C3%BA-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng/poem-rGUUvKyr7qpQkgtUjsBV6w">Vịnh tú chướng - 詠繡障</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-L%E1%BB%87nh-N%C4%83ng/author-NQboKNumscuMTrMsx-MrUg">Hồ Lệnh Năng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
